        "  FrameViewSDK   - Framerate and latency benchmarking",
        "  NvVAD          - NVIDIA virtual audio device (streaming)",
        "  MSVCRT         - Bundled VC++ redistributable (install extras/vcredist2022 if needed)",
        "",
        "To remove this driver, use Display Driver Uninstaller: 'scoop install ddu'"
